
	Death lotto!
        --------------------------------------------------------  
        The game is administrated by Ash. 
        This is a game of chance.
        Ash will give tell you when to take your chance ie 'dice'.
        IF you roll higher then the other participants you win.
         *The winner gets a free level for each participant.
        Otherwise you die (no gear loss).
        Send a tell to Ash when hes running lotto to play.



